    "body": "I think this is a serde issue on ethabi, which emits `constant: false` even if we set it to `None`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rust-ethereum/ethabi/blob/199e307462ea6ad17c3ff48dcba8aa42b23cb2c3/ethabi/src/function.rs#L31-L35\r\n\r\ninstead of `serde(default)` in should be `#[serde(default, skip_serializing_if = \"Option::is_none\")]`\r\n\r\nI think we can ignore `constant` entirely at this point @brockelmore ?",
